+// Altivec-optimized SHA1 in C. This is tested on ppc64le only.
+//
+// References:
+// https://software.intel.ccom/en-us/articles/improving-the-performance-of-the-secure-hash-algorithm-1
+// http://arctic.org/~dean/crypto/sha1.html
+//
